            mod_id, 
            author_id,
            date, 
            downloads_total,
            views,
            followers,
            favorited,
            votes_up,
            votes_down,
            score,
            num_comments,
            playtime,
            time_updated,
            version
        )
        SELECT * FROM UNNEST(
            $1::text[], 
            $2::text[],
            $3::date[], 
            $4::int[], 
            $5::bigint[],
